s\", \"from\": 2602, \"to\": 2617}, {\"ngram\": \"success\", \"from\": 2621, \"to\": 2628}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was more forthcoming after failing to make the 100 metres final on Sunday night, saying: \\\"I am disappointed.\", \"from\": 2677, \"to\": 2788, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 100 metres\", \"from\": 2723, \"to\": 2737}, {\"ngram\": \"Sunday night\", \"from\": 2747, \"to\": 2759}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I gave it my best.\", \"from\": 2789, \"to\": 2807, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You all know I had a hamstring injury.\", \"from\": 2808, \"to\": 2846, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a hamstring injury\", \"from\": 2827, \"to\": 2845}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It is not the easiest thing to come back from, especially what I had, a grade two on the outside of the (right) hamstring.\", \"from\": 2848, \"to\": 2971, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the easiest thing\", \"from\": 2859, \"to\": 2876}, {\"ngram\": \"especially what\", \"from\": 2896, \"to\": 2911}, {\"ngram\": \"a grade\", \"from\": 2919, \"to\": 2926}, {\"ngram\": \"the outside\", \"from\": 2934, \"to\": 2945}, {\"ngram\": \"the (right) hamstring\", \"from\": 2949, \"to\": 2970}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Not getting enough races to be race sharp, that was my issue.\", \"from\": 2973, \"to\": 3035, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"enough races\", \"from\": 2986, \"to\": 2998}, {\"ngram\": \"my issue\", \"from\": 3026, \"to\": 3034}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Everything had to be rushed.\", \"from\": 3036, \"to\": 3064, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Everything\", \"from\": 3036, \"to\": 3046}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After the injury you start to get the treatment right away.\", \"from\": 3065, \"to\": 3124, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the injury\", \"from\": 3071, \"to\": 3081}, {\"ngram\": \"the treatment\", \"from\": 3099, \"to\": 3112}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If we had more races, you know that I am a better performer than this.\", \"from\": 3126, \"to\": 3197, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more races\", \"from\": 3137, \"to\": 3147}, {\"ngram\": \"a better performer\", \"from\": 3168, \"to\": 3186}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Last year we ended with 9.88 on the podium and with a bronze.\", \"from\": 3198, \"to\": 3259, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the podium\", \"from\": 3230, \"to\": 3240}, {\"ngram\": \"a bronze\", \"from\": 3250, \"to\": 3258}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I know what I am capable of.\", \"from\": 3261, \"to\": 3290, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I had to be battling with an injury.\", \"from\": 3291, \"to\": 3327, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an injury\", \"from\": 3317, \"to\": 3326}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It kind of sucks, last minute just before the Olympics, but I am a fighter.\", \"from\": 3329, \"to\": 3405, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3372, \"to\": 3384}, {\"ngram\": \"a fighter\", \"from\": 3395, \"to\": 3404}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am very determined, and that's why I wanted to give it a go.\", \"from\": 3406, \"to\": 3468, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a go\", \"from\": 3463, \"to\": 3467}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I got the training in but the races is what I needed to get me race sharp.\", \"from\": 3470, \"to\": 3545, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the training\", \"from\": 3477, \"to\": 3489}, {\"ngram\": \"the races\", \"from\": 3497, \"to\": 3506}, {\"ngram\": \"race\", \"from\": 3534, \"to\": 3538}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"As a competitive athlete, you want to be a part of the mix.\", \"from\": 3547, \"to\": 3607, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a competitive athlete\", \"from\": 3551, \"to\": 3572}, {\"ngram\": \"a part\", \"from\": 3589, \"to\": 3595}, {\"ngram\": \"the mix\", \"from\": 3599, \"to\": 3606}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I rarely miss out on finals, so this is one a bit hard to swallow.\", \"from\": 3608, \"to\": 3674, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"finals\", \"from\": 3629, \"to\": 3635}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I will just move on from here.\", \"from\": 3676, \"to\": 3707, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The road sometimes can be rocky, there are days that you guys do not see the work behind the scenes and injuries that come along.\", \"from\": 3708, \"to\": 3837, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The road\", \"from\": 3708, \"to\": 3716}, {\"ngram\": \"days\", \"from\": 3751, \"to\": 3755}, {\"ngram\": \"you guys\", \"from\": 3761, \"to\": 3769}, {\"ngram\": \"the work\", \"from\": 3781, \"to\": 3789}, {\"ngram\": \"the scenes\", \"from\": 3797, \"to\": 3807}, {\"ngram\": \"injuries\", \"from\": 3812, \"to\": 3820}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We try to give our best.\", \"from\": 3838, \"to\": 3862, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Today I gave it my best.\\\"\", \"from\": 3863, \"to\": 3888, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Join thought-provoking conversations, follow other Independent readers and see their replies Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in\", \"from\": 3890, \"to\": 4120, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3941, \"end\": 3952, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 1.3549199618487265e-13, \"text\": \"Independent\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"thought-provoking conversations\", \"from\": 3895, \"to\": 3926}, {\"ngram\": \"their replies\", \"from\": 3969, \"to\": 3982}, {\"ngram\": \"the page\", \